   SOURCE_URL[0]=http://alx14.free.fr/burncenter/download/$SOURCE
        WEB_SITE=http://alx14.free.fr/burncenter/
         ENTERED=20050119
         UPDATED=20050119
  SOURCE_HASH[0]=sha512:61c5c8f520acba1138bb039127439e7919e9d8dc77e39bb547e0fb6d25b595cfd23cca77b0040293ced494d13f02a1cf12fb3be97ae1ed7b73b7b22fd1ed2cce       
      LICENSE[0]=GPL
           SHORT="Text-based interface to cd-burning tools"
cat << EOF
Burncenter is a very easy-to-use perl module, and text-based interface to cd-burning tools under UNIX (cdrecord/burncd, cdda2wav, mkisofs). 

Features

    * easy to use text interface
    * transparent multi-session support
    * creation of audio cd from WAVE or MP3 files, or from playlists
    * data and audio cd copy support
    * cdrw support (fast and complete blanking)
EOF
